summary: Electrical Engineer able to perform several functions combining management, technical and commercial capabilities. Experience offering (type) testing services for power equipment, as well as customized solutions for energy distribution, and control systems. Project management experience from consultancy and basic engineering throughout commissioning. Enthusiast to learn and to collaborate assertively within international, multicultural, multidisciplinary teams. Interested in innovative solutions for energy efficiency and clean energy.
